title: The Wine Show S01E01 PDTV.x264-JIVE.mp4
description:
Matthew Goode & Matthew Rhys star in this brand new 13 x 1 hour television series. Filmed in beautiful locations all over the world, The Wine Show is informative, entertaining, humorous and surprising, with something for everyone who enjoys a glass of wine.




The Wine Show - Series 1, Episode 1


Actors Matthew Goode and Matthew Rhys present a guide to wine from an Italian villa. They attend a barrel race in Tuscany, and are joined by chef Brad McDonald.


Original Air Date: 10-Apr-2016
